edu.ncsu.csc216.wolf_results.util

Class ArrayList

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.ncsu.csc216.wolf_results.util.ArrayList
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    List

    public class ArrayList
extends java.lang.Object
implements List
    creates and maintains a custom arraylist that knows its size and members can resize, add, edits and removes elements. does not allow duplicate items to be added.
